Where to Watch

George Clooney, Brad Pitt and Julia Roberts head an all-star cast in Steven Soderbergh's slick remake of the 1960 Rat Pack caper. Clooney plays ex-con Danny Ocean, who rounds up a crew of talented criminals to rob three Las Vegas casinos. The gambling palaces are owned by Terry Benedict (Andy Garcia)---the boyfriend of Danny's ex (Roberts). Matt Damon, Don Cheadle, Carl Reiner, Elliot Gould, Angie Dickinson, Henry Silva.
